            "post_author_verified": true,
            "post_time": "10h ago",
            "post_text": "<p>I just finished this book and it is amazing. It woke me up inside, I found myself again but better. I feel new energy and hope, like I've had an awakening, a renewal in my mind, body and spirit. I'm excited to try some things I think I always felt but didn't understand until now. Get this book, you won't regret it!</p>",
