            "post_author": "Jennifer Thompson",
            "post_author_avatar": "shopify://shop_images/openart-a-hyper-realistic-full-body-portrait-of-a-beautiful-19-year-old-lonodon-gi_430x_99a8b6ab-bde8-4986-9a20-6d5ff9b5af0a.webp",
            "post_author_verified": true,
            "post_time": "2h ago",
            "post_text": "<p>Frequency Beneath The Field by Amara Callen is one of the most profound books I’ve ever read on personal transformation. It goes far beyond simple “positive thinking.” It blends ancient wisdom with modern science to show how to truly align your energy and intentions. The exercises are practical, the insights are deep, and the auhor’s sincerity shines through every page.</p>",
