            "post_author_verified": false,
            "post_time": "14d ago",
            "post_text": "<p>My Gratitude to Amara Callen for this book that clearly presented the thoughts I needed during a grieving time.<br/>Faith and reality became empowered as I followed the practical applications.<br/>Joy awakened as I aligned with the sacred truths.<br/>This book is a valued read and re-read in my library.<br/><br/></p>",
