        },
        "collapsible_row_NKT6W7": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How quickly will I see results?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Most readers of Frequency Beneath The Field report measurable changes within 7–14 days when following the protocols correctly. Results depend on consistent daily practice.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_zrBznN": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do I need meditation experience?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Not at all. The system is designed for busy professionals with no meditation background. The longest daily practice is just 10 minutes.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_7HLMd7": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What if this doesn’t work for me?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>You’re protected by our 30-day money-back guarantee. If you don’t see improvements in your manifestation results, you’ll get a full refund, no questions asked.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_FMLRVT": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is this compatible with my religious beliefs?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Yes. This system focuses on brain science and neurological patterns, not spiritual or religious concepts. It’s purely scientific methodology.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_tRymFP": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How is this different from other manifestation programs I’ve tried?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Frequency Beneath The Field was designed by Amara Callen specifically to align with your brain’s unique patterns. Generic programs fail because they ignore individual neurological differences.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_4Qwtyj": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What if I’m too busy for another self-help program?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>The entire daily protocol takes just 10 minutes. No lengthy meditations or complex rituals—just precise alignment techniques designed for busy professionals.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_LwLPbM": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do I need any special equipment or apps?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>No. Everything works with just the materials provided. You don’t need meditation cushions, crystals, vision boards, or any additional purchases.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_cHmdBc": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "I’m very analytical – will this make sense to me?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Absolutely. Frequency Beneath The Field was designed specifically for analytical minds. You’ll understand exactly <strong>why</strong> each technique works, eliminating doubt and maximizing results.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_FjRjCT": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What format are the materials in?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>All materials are digital (PDF and audio files) for instant access. You can read on any device and listen to audio sessions anywhere.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_9cU8HW": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is there ongoing support or is this a one-time purchase?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>This is a complete system with everything you need. No monthly fees, upsells, or required coaching calls. You own it permanently.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_4DqqLF": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What if I’ve failed at manifestation before?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Previous failures likely happened because you were using methods designed for different brain patterns. Amara Callen’s system is calibrated specifically for how <strong>your brain</strong> processes reality creation.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_3GMCLH": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I know I’m actually aligned with The Lost Laws of Manifestation?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>You’ll take a simple assessment that analyzes your responses against established neurological patterns. This identifies your specific manifestation type based on your answers.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_rpick8": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I share this with my spouse/partner?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>The materials are for your personal use. Your partner would need their own copy, as they may have a different manifestation type requiring different protocols.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_WiVX6c": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What if I’m skeptical about manifestation in general?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Perfect. Frequency Beneath The Field was designed specifically for skeptical, science-minded people. Your analytical nature is actually an advantage for this frequency-based approach.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_UwDEcR": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long do I have access to the materials?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Lifetime access. Download everything immediately and keep forever. No expiration dates or recurring fees.</p>",
